{"tid":765503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個幾痴線幾無救嘅政府至會容許呢種事發生?","createTime":"2018-08-02T21:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T14:33:37.000Z","uid":47659,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"19ed4788a0bed097a1620868cfb66f4a0b0dd6d6","tid":765503,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T21:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180801/20465814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F20465814&d=BjdueF2Fu17egHyAgZSgizCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=14c7af07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F20465814&h=d7edb0dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180801/20465814</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n18年前入境處縱火主謀生活富貴<br />\n2018-08-01223.9K<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次非首次有人到政府部門縱火或企圖縱火，其中18年前發生的入境處縱火案釀成2死44傷更轟動全城，案中主腦施君龍被判謀殺罪成，後改判誤殺，服刑5年便出獄，更於2011年獲批單程證來港。<br />\n2000年8月，24歲的施君龍與一批爭取居港權的內地人於灣仔入境事務大樓1301室示威，當時施曾對入境處職員指「出年今日係你哋死忌」，並揚言要將入境處職員「變燒豬」，其間有人淋天拿水及點火，由於起火地點接近房門，加上房間狹小，40多人擠在房內無法逃生，42歲高級入境主任梁錦光及26歲示威者林小星被燒死。<br />\n<br />\n2011年獲批單程證<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕施及另外6人，施被控以兩項謀殺罪，判處終身監禁；另外6名被告則因誤殺及縱火罪成，被判監12至13年。7人其後上訴，施被改判誤殺罪，獲減刑至8年，於2005年底出獄，被遣返內地後，2011年獲批單程證來港，在本港開設投資公司及擔任家庭團聚互助會新界分會董事，被揭發生活富貴。2014年，司法界大遊行促中央撤回白皮書，施到場辱罵在場法律人士為「走狗、漢奸」。對於縱火案主謀成本港永久居民，梁錦光兒子曾向傳媒發電郵，批評此舉會增加社會危險及不安，促政府檢視單程證審批制度。<br />\n■記者潘婉玲"},{"pid":"a6a44a2b17713eb43bac019a3e595bb56c11b37b","tid":765503,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9香港"},{"pid":"834b72499e8686c498f6596041d745745245b8fd","tid":765503,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a655ff236679cc8b01c8b3abd18e4e971d948ec4","tid":765503,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"今日先知？<br />\n97以後再無香港政府"},{"pid":"50a3a3fdd1f450beae810a990eb9b84f717c634e","tid":765503,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a655ff236679cc8b01c8b3abd18e4e971d948ec4","tid":765503,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"今日先知？<br />\n97以後再無香港政府"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"竟然咁都可以拎單程證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f50c892b68a60c0b67e3e6ef50ae67691b5819b","tid":765503,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7446c0be67e870f0db4c78189205e10ba0fafc6","tid":765503,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40fd0180db483b768f5a55fe8af2913c49a68875","tid":765503,"uid":185126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"坐得仲短過梁天琦<br />\n明明死咗兩個人<br />\n打正大陸旗號真係永遠無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957786a72b7df270df01efb9495ac9f399e7d1b3","tid":765503,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3292bd72fddec30fce89d0e50d5737808e231ede","tid":765503,"uid":5267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:0